## What

Adds [monapi](https://monapi.dev) to the x402 ecosystem page.

## About monapi

monapi is a free, open-source SDK that wraps the entire x402 integration into a single function call. It supports Express, Next.js, and MCP.

Instead of manually configuring CAIP-2 network IDs, token contract addresses, scheme registration, and facilitator communication, developers write:

```typescript
import { monapi } from "@monapi/sdk";

app.use(monapi({
  wallet: process.env.WALLET,
  price: 0.01,
}));
